Definition: biometric identification by scanning a person's face and matching it against a library of known faces
Example: they used face recognition to spot known terrorists
Synonyms: facial_recognition, automatic_face_recognition, biometric_identification, noun, act, terrorism, c, biometric, identification, by, scanning, a, person, s, face, and, matching, it, against, library, of, known, faces, they, used, recognition, to, spot, terrorists
Category: noun.communication
